---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Links AI" description="Links AI helps service businesses turn recurring work into practical AI systems that are built, launched, and improved over time." pageClass="page-home">
  <section class="hero" slot="hero">
    <h1>We build practical AI systems for service businesses.</h1>
    <p>
      We help you find the right place to start, build the system,
      and keep improving it once it is live.
    </p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book an exploratory call</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Find the right starting point</h3>
        <p>We look for the workflows where AI can create real operational value, not just novelty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Build around your operation</h3>
        <p>We design systems around the way your business already works, using the tools your team already depends on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Launch something useful</h3>
        <p>We focus on working systems that reduce manual work, improve response time, and make your operation easier to run.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Improve over time</h3>
        <p>We stay involved after launch so the system keeps getting better as your business changes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Three ways to explore Links AI</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>How it works</h3>
        <p>See what it looks like to work with us from first call through launch and ongoing improvement.</p>
        <p><a href="/how-it-works">View the customer journey →</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Services</h3>
        <p>Understand the offer ladder: where we start, what we build, and how we support it long term.</p>
        <p><a href="/services">View services →</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Insights</h3>
        <p>Read practical thinking on AI operations, workflow design, and where businesses should start.</p>
        <p><a href="/insights">Read insights →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-box">
    <h2>Want to find the best place to start?</h2>
    <p>Tell us how your business runs today. We will help you identify the highest-value next move.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Request a call</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
